            "heading": "The Ultimate Guide to Mattress Foundations: Box Springs, Adjustable Beds, and More",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_bcRpBJ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>Introduction</h2><p>A solid mattress foundation is essential for a good night’s sleep. Not only does it support your mattress, but it also improves comfort, extends your mattress’s lifespan, and enhances the overall look of your bedroom. Whether you’re considering a traditional box spring, an adjustable bed base, or a modern platform foundation, this guide will help you understand your options and choose the right one for your needs. For more tips on setting up your sleep space, be sure to check out our <a href=\"https://mattressville.ca/pages/mattress-buying-guide\">Mattress Buying Guide</a>.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
